==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ʌrəʊ|-ʌrəʊ]]

===Noun===
'''furrow'''
# A line cut in the soil, especially when [[plow]]ed in order to plant a [[crop]].
#: ''We had to walk across the deep '''furrows''' in the field.''
# A deep line in the skin of the face,  especially on someone's [[forehead]].
#: ''When she was tired, a deep '''furrow''' appeared on her forehead.''

